    "name": "OS2 User Management Service — L1 API Tests",
    "description": "Layer 1: API Testing for gw-user-mgmt-svc\n\nComprehensive endpoint validation:\n- Happy path (14 endpoints)\n- Error boundary tests (400, 401, 403, 404, 422)\n- Idempotency validation\n- Schema assertions\n\nExecution: newman run OS2-User-Mgmt-L1-API-Tests.postman_collection.json --environment env.dev.json",
